msgid "Security"
msgstr "🔐 Sécurité"

#: app/templates/help.html:39
msgid "Grylli encrypts sensitive data and logs all key actions for auditing."
msgstr ""
"Grylli chiffre les données sensibles et journalise toutes les actions clés "
